<p>Want to make transaction which contains next functionality </p>  <ol> <li>Read from data from storage</li> <li>transform data "scala functions"</li> <li>convert transformed data to the JSON</li> <li>send to the API</li> <li>get response </li> </ol>  <p>Can I wrap all steps 1 - 5 to the transaction ?<br> And can I roll back the transaction if on the step 5 the response will be an error ? </p>  <p>Has Scala native tools for transaction management? Any alternatives? </p>